OL,6,FA former detective who stalked her ex-
OL,7,Fpartner and tried to ruin his surfing
OL,8,Fbusiness by posting "untrue and
OL,9,Fseriously alarming" accusations on
OL,10,Fsocial media has avoided an immediate
OL,11,Fjail term.
OL,13,FSue Thorpe, 44, a former officer with
OL,14,FNorthumbria Police, bombarded surfing
OL,15,Finstructor Barry Henderson with
OL,16,Fabusive voicemails, texts and emails
OL,17,Fin a year-long harassment campaign
OL,18,Fafter he ended their relationship.
