OL,6,FShe also used the police national
OL,7,Fcomputer to illegally look up
OL,8,Finformation about Mr Henderson
OL,9,Ffollowing the split.
OL,11,FOn Wednesday, Thorpe, of Whitley Bay,
OL,12,FNorth Tyneside, was sentenced to two
OL,13,Fyears in prison, suspended for two
OL,14,Fyears after being found guilty of
OL,15,Fstalking and misuse of computer data.
