OL,6,FShe was also ordered to carry out 120
OL,7,Fhours of unpaid work, 20
OL,8,Frehabilitation activity days and
OL,9,Fhanded a 10-year restraining order
OL,10,Fbanning her from any contact with Mr
OL,11,FHenderson.
OL,13,FNewcastle Crown Court heard that
OL,14,Fbetween June 2020 and September 2021,
OL,15,FThorpe sent Mr Henderson messages
OL,16,Faccusing him of being violent towards
OL,17,Fher during their five-year-long
OL,18,Frelationship and posted "untrue and
OL,19,Fseriously alarming" allegations about
OL,20,Fhim.
