OL,6,FA judge was told she repeated these
OL,7,Fclaims to his friends, family members
OL,8,Fand new partner, and tried to harm his
OL,9,Fsurfing business by posting them on
OL,10,FFacebook and to a charity his business
OL,11,Fworked with.
OL,13,FThorpe set up a fake email address to
OL,14,Fcontact other organisations with her
OL,15,Faccusations, at one point pretending
OL,16,Fto be a concerned parent, and turned
OL,17,Fup at his workplace twice, it was said.
