OL,6,FIn a victim impact statement read in
OL,7,Fcourt, Mr Henderson said Thorpe was
OL,8,F"on a mission to destroy him" and her
OL,9,Fclaims made him feel "physically sick"
OL,10,Fwhen he read them.
OL,12,FThe statement read: "Sue is clearly
OL,13,Ftrying to ruin my life and make my day
OL,14,Fto day living a nightmare.
OL,16,F"It is embarrassing and humiliating
OL,17,Fhaving to explain to family and
OL,18,Ffriends what is happening.
OL,20,F"What Sue has done has created a
OL,21,Fmassive strain on my personal life."
