OL,6,FJudge Amanda Rippon said Thorpe, who
OL,7,Fhad been a police officer for 19
OL,8,Fyears, had suffered a miscarriage of
OL,9,Ftwins following IVF and the offending
OL,10,Fhappened "at a time of her life when
OL,11,Fshe was in crisis and ill".
